name: MeinaAlter
description:
MeinaAlter doesn't have an objective. It serves as a way for me to upload models that doesn't fit in the other 4 Meinas.

I created a discord server where you can post images that you generated, discuss prompt and/or ask for help. https://discord.gg/F6yeQtEQ98 ( i'll be helping and answering questions there whenever i can! )

If you like one of my models and want to support their updates:
I have a ko-fi and Patreon page where you can support me or buy me a coffee <3 , it will be very much appreciated: https://ko-fi.com/meina and https://www.patreon.com/MeinaMix

MeinaAlter and the other of Meinas will ALWAYS be FREE.

The images in the samples aren't cherry picked, if i had spent 2h to cherry pick each of the images it would hide how the model really performs and i don't think thats fair.

The recommendations are just basic guidelines, you're welcome to use your own parameters or change them to your liking!!


Recommendations of use:
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Enable Quantization in K samplers.

Add ' Realistic ' and/or ' Photorealistic ' as first token of the prompt to have 2.5d feeling in the images.

Hires.fix is needed to drastically improve the quality of face and eyes!
All of the sample images were generated in 512x1024 and upscaled 2x twice, hires and extra.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Recommendations:
Sampler: Euler a, 40 to 60 steps.

Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras, 30 to 60 steps.
CFG Scale: 7.
Resolutions: 512x768, 512x1024 for Portrait!
Resolutions: 768x512, 1024x512, 1536x512 for Landscape!
Hires.fix: R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B , with 10 to 30 steps at 0.3 up to 0.5 denoising.
Clip Skip: 2.
Negatives: ' (worst quality, low quality:1.4), monochrome, zombie, (interlocked fingers:1.4), '
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

modelVersions.name: V1
modelVersions.description:
This version have BAKED VAE.
In the generation data it will say PastelV4 because thats a scrapped update from my pastel mode.
( all of the images in the samples are upscaled by 2x using SDwebui extras tab.)

If you have any questions related to the model, samples, how to get started or just want to share your creations, feel free to join my newly created discord: https://discord.gg/XC9nGZNDUd <3

Hires.fix is not a need in order to make decent images, but it will improve images where the face is far away, as in full body images and others alike.
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Recommendations of use:

-- Enable Quantization in K samplers.
-- Clip skip 2.

Negatives: ' (worst quality, low quality:1.4), monochrome, zombie, '

For resolutions 512x1024 or higher:
-- SDE Karass - 30 steps

-- Hires: Anime6B or None ,0.3 denoising,10 steps.

For Resolutions 512x768 or lower and Landscape:

-- Euler a - 15~60 steps.
-- DPM++ 2S a Karass - 50~60 steps.
-- DPM++ 2M a karass - 25~30 steps.

-- Hires: Latent, 0.55 denoising, 10 steps.
( latent upscaler will often make hands or limbs look worse )
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This model is a merge of MeinaPastelV3 as base, 0.9 of epinoiseoffset, and redistributed the weights using MeinaMix V5.1 to fix the hands.
